&lt;h4>&#xD;
    Immutability of Scrum&#xD;
&lt;/h4>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Scrumâ€™s roles, artifacts, events, and rules are immutable and although implementing only parts of Scrum is possible,&#xD;
    the result is not Scrum. Scrum exists only in its entirety and functions well as a container for other techniques,&#xD;
    methodologies, and practices.&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
